        "uid": "90852"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t大约是受到一位叫「弐瓶勉」的漫画家的影响。<br/>\n<br/>\n弐瓶专门画科幻漫画，他好几作品，如《BLAME!》和《希德尼娅的骑士》等里面都出现了名叫「東亜重工」的神秘组织，作中许多装备都是这家公司生产的。<br/>\n<br/>\n吉丰重工那个最明显，连字体都是模仿漫画里东亚重工的字体。<br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLnB4aW1nLm5ldC9pbWctbWFzdGVyL2ltZy8yMDA5LzAyLzE1LzA5LzEyLzI1LzMxMDY0NTlfcDBfbWFzdGVyMTIwMC5qcGc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.pximg.net/img-master/img/2009/02/15/09/12/25/3106459_p0_master1200.jpg\">https://i.pximg.net/img-master/img/2009/02/15/09/12/25/3106459_p0_master1200.jpg</a> </div>",
      "date": "2024-04-14",
      "agree_count": 1,
